<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200908/fa5cc2ee01fa4380958f9dfcebd95023.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来源：友邦保险中期业绩报告</p>
